body:
I'm going to close this issue for now since, as you pointed out the `CostGraphDef` is available from the `RunMetadata`. However, if profiling your graph is what is driving you, you might also want to consider [tracing](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/1824#issuecomment-225754659)

Please feel free to re-open if your concerns weren't addressed
